title: Sound & Vision - (Magazine) April-May 2009
description: Overview: Sound and Vision Magazine provides authoratative tests and reviews of home theater equipment such as HDTVs, surround sound speakers, home theater systems, Blu-ray and HD DVD players, LCD and Plasma TVs, amps and preamps, speakers and subwoofers and more. Get helpful tips on how to buy an HDTV, how to install HDTV in your home, and how to get the most out of your av system.
